                                              <Properties>
                                                <Property name="messageText" type="java.lang.String" value="&lt;html&gt;Enter an image prefix or select an image or meta file. Examples of valid search patterns:&lt;br&gt;- .\u005cinvocations\u005cexport\u005cnewinvocation&lt;br&gt;- .\u005cinvocations\u005cexport\u005cnewinvocation-frame&lt;br&gt;- .\u005cinvocations\u005cexport\u005cnewinvocation-frame-0&lt;br&gt;-.\u005cinvocations\u005cexport\u005cnewinvocation-frame-3.png&lt;br&gt;- .\u005cinvocations\u005cexport\u005cnewinvocation.meta&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Supported image formats: PNG or GIF. Automatically detects valid image formats that match the file pattern.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Color format should be 4BPP / 16 indexed colors. Images of 8BPP / 256 indexed colors will be converted to 4 BPP / 16 (some colors may be lost).&lt;br&gt;Colors will be convered to CRAM format (the color format used by the SEGA Genesis).&lt;br&gt;Color index 0 is treated as transparent.&lt;/html&gt;" containsInvalidXMLChars="true"/>
